<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page d'Accueil</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .hero-section, .second-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 50px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: white;
            background: #ff6600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #cc5500;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .icon-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .icon-group i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #52566f;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .icon-group i:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section, .second-section {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .content {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .image-container img {
                width: 80%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Penser durablement et stratégiquement !</h1>
                <p>Faites la différence face à la concurrence. Investissez dans l’avenir et soyez compétitif dès aujourd’hui.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">En savoir plus</a>
            </div>
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="image1.png" alt="Illustration Business">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="second-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="image2.png" alt="Illustration Business 2">
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Optimisez votre performance digitale</h1>
                <p>Développez votre présence en ligne et améliorez votre visibilité grâce à des stratégies digitales efficaces.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Découvrir nos services</a>
                <div class="icon-group">
                    <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
                    <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
